features: HIGH QUALITY WELL-MADE PAPER PARTY BAGS – Our Small Twist handle Paper Party Bag size is 18 x 22 x 8cm. They are made from thick Kraft paper which is tough and scratch resistance. Our paper gift bags have a strong and reliable load-bearing capacity for all uses.

WIDE RANGE OF COLOUR CHOICES – Available in 14 Fantastic bright colours including Yellow, Fuchsia, Hot Pink, White, Brown, Black, Red, Light Blue, Blue, Light Green, Green, Orange, Silver and Gold. Our bags offer a vibrant and colourful eye-catching selection for your event. Whether you need them for a kid’s party, a special birthday, festivals, anniversaries, wedding, baby shower, your small business or even a corporate giveaway you can find a colour that matches your theme or brand identity.

STRONG STURDY TWIST PAPER HANDLES – Twist handle carrier bags provide a convenient and comfortable way to carry them. They offer a firm grip and ergonomic design which enhances the overall usability and practicality of these bags. Our bag sizes do not include the size of the handles.

PERFECT FOR CRAFT – All our bags are single colour with no patterns, no frills. Our Gift Bags are the perfect canvas for your own DIY creation. Transfer your imagination and creativity to make every bag a one-of-a-kind for the perfect Gift or extra special child’s party. Suitable to contain any present, gift or party favours including little toys, notes, dolls, cake, biscuits, sweets and other present ideas.

ECO-FRIENDLY PAPER GIFT BAGS – Thepaperbagstore paper bags are made of premium recyclable paper. They are environment-friendly, durable, and reusable. Eco-friendly and great for giving to friends and family at your special event. They are also great for packing gifts, groceries, your small business merchandise. Our paper bags are recyclable, compostable, and a great alternative to plastic bags.
